      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BE GRACIOUS (5) was a strong winner (19.53) from box 2 last time, scoring by 2.75 lengths at this track. Has a tricky draw to overcome and will need a clean break. Can make it two on the bounce. LILY MARLEEN (1) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at Warragul over 400m behind Vinnie's Camel (23.88) in a Grade 5. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Has ability and is one of the better chances. PAW FAROK (2) gave a start after copping a check in running and missed the frame when a 25 length seventh (24.12) at Shepparton in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. Has the ability and can measure up. AUSSIE SAVANNAH (3) finished in the placings last start and deserves some thought.",
